    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/cc17257ab2638f73158ca512904fb793.poster.avif?t=1771863174\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/cc17257ab2638f73158ca512904fb793.webm?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/cc17257ab2638f73158ca512904fb793.mp4?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘奥回响》是一款roguelite动作RPG游戏，游戏中所有力量皆赋予你手。你将创造法术、优化战术、开辟属于自己的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演记忆轮回的守护者马扎里姆，回到秘奥王国的魔法世界。邂逅王国的居民，对抗缠绕它的过去阴影。在与遗忘的斗争中，世界的记忆将指引你前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/f5f64743f0af41ae960fe2d4e42f546a.poster.avif?t=1771863174\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/f5f64743f0af41ae960fe2d4e42f546a.webm?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/f5f64743f0af41ae960fe2d4e42f546a.mp4?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情体验《秘奥法师》饱受好评的法术创造系统的进化吧。发现编织记忆魔法的精妙艺术，创造无限多样且具有强大联动效果的法术。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨练战术、提升实力，创造出有效的法术，直面可怕的头目和生物。你的每一步旅程都将使你朝着精通魔法的道路上更近一步。准备好迎接决定秘奥王国记忆命运的史诗战斗吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/076a12d37673b28ebf46728d8d7b42c5.poster.avif?t=1771863174\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/076a12d37673b28ebf46728d8d7b42c5.webm?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/076a12d37673b28ebf46728d8d7b42c5.mp4?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开辟你的道路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遗忘正在秘奥王国蔓延。它遍布道路、村庄、湖泊和群山。拯救世界记忆的旅程注定是充满陷阱和邂逅的史诗之行。你会选择哪条道路，是最简单的还是最有回报的？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/3a1e32a1d7bdf38a2c81133b89110fee.poster.avif?t=1771863174\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/3a1e32a1d7bdf38a2c81133b89110fee.webm?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/3a1e32a1d7bdf38a2c81133b89110fee.mp4?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现你的内在魔法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每找到一段记忆都是通向平衡和启迪的一步。在这款激动人心的动作冒险游戏中，抓住你的魔法命运，探索这个神秘的世界。每次与居民的相遇、每次与过去阴影的战斗都会增强你与这个迷人王国深厚根基的联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你探索神秘土地和面对挑战时，你将收集记忆，这些记忆将揭示你自己的故事与秘奥王国命运之间的联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/0233b1cb985886850d60c10109d95613.poster.avif?t=1771863174\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/0233b1cb985886850d60c10109d95613.webm?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/974480/extras/0233b1cb985886850d60c10109d95613.mp4?t=1771863174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拯救秘奥王国的记忆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村民和城镇居民需要你的帮助来恢复他们的记忆。完成任务即可揭示秘密并获得奖励。随着你的冒险，世界地图会不断演变，以对应不断推进的故事情节。</p>",
